Package: wizrd
Type: Package
Title: Integration of Large Language Models (LLMs) into R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Michael", family = "Lawrence", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "michafla@gene.com")
)
Description: The wizrd package integrates Large Language Models (LLMs) within
	     the R session to enhance data analysis and package development.
	     It allows users to leverage the power of LLMs for generating code,
	     guiding data exploration, and creating documentation.
License: MIT
